<t:admin.Layout t:pageTitle="CampaignList" t:navigation="管理员管理 > 详细信息" pageGroup="system" xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_0_0.xsd">
    <body>
    	<table style="BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse;width:100%" borderColor="#ced5b1" 
            cellSpacing="0" cellPadding="0" width="100%" border="1">
			<tr>
				<td class="green_bg" colspan="3"><strong>广告主详细信息</strong></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">用户名</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.name} 
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">用户昵称</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.nickName} 
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">用户组</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userGroup.name} 
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="green_bg" colspan="2">公司信息</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">公司名称</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.company} 
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">公司介绍</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.description} 
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">联系人名称</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.contact} 
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">国家</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.country}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">地区</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.state}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">县/市/区</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.city}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">联系地址</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.city}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">邮政编码</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.city}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">电话号码</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.city}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">手机号码</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.city}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">QQ号码</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.city}
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="greenwithe_bg">MSN帐号</td>
				<td class="greenwithe">
				    ${user.userInfo.city}
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<div class="center">
			<input type="button" onclick="window.location.href='/admin/usermanage/editPage/${user.id}'" value="edit" />
			<input type="button" onclick="window.location.href='/admin/usermanage/ClientlistPage'" value="back" />
		</div>
    </body>
</t:admin.Layout>